spec_data.Name: snakeyaml
spec_data.Description:
SnakeYAML features:
    * a complete YAML 1.1 parser. In particular,
      SnakeYAML can parse all examples from the specification.
    * Unicode support including UTF-8/UTF-16 input/output.
    * high-level API for serializing and deserializing
      native Java objects.
    * support for all types from the YAML types repository.
    * relatively sensible error messages.

spec_data.Summary: YAML parser and emitter for the Java programming language
